<p>As I found <code>SELECT * FROM t INTO my_data;</code> works only if:</p>  <pre><code>DO $$ DECLARE my_data t%ROWTYPE; BEGIN SELECT * FROM t INTO my_data WHERE id = ?; END $$; </code></pre>  <p>Am I right?</p>  <p>If I want to get only 2-3 columns instead of all columns. How can I define <code>my_data</code>?</p>  <p>That is,</p>  <pre><code>DO $$ DECLARE my_data &lt;WHAT HERE??&gt;; BEGIN SELECT id,name,surname FROM t INTO my_data WHERE id = ?; END $$; </code></pre>